Class Device

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.model.device.Device
All Implemented Interfaces:
Observer
Direct Known Subclasses:
AirConditioner, CoffeeMachine, FeederForPet, Fridge, Lamp, MusicCenter, PC, Shower, TV
public abstract class Device extends Object implements Observer

This class describes (model) the abstract class of devices : Device and this class implements Design Pattern Observer
